<h2 class="gem-c-heading  gem-c-heading--mobile-top-margin  " id="details-title">Details</h2>


<div aria-labelledby="details-title">
  
<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak direction-ltr" data-module="govspeak">
      <div class="govspeak">
<p>We want to give you a service that is even-handed, accurate and based on mutual trust and respect. We also want to make it as easy as we can for you to get things right.</p>

<p>In partnership with Royal Association for Deaf people, we’ve produced a short video presented in British Sign Language which explains Your Charter.</p>

<p><a rel="external" href="https://youtu.be/UIL-VKoWmws">HMRC - Your Charter - BSL version</a></p>

<h2 id="your-charter---annual-reports">Your Charter - annual reports</h2>

<p>Each year, we <a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/your-charter-annual-reports">publish a report</a> on how we perform against the standards set out in Your Charter.</p>
</div>
</div>

